14_44	0.096696433	Bean agrees that some of the plans are ``lousy,'' but says they can produce net gains.
14_45	0.075587286	``HCPs have the potential to produce results that are far better than we could otherwise expect,'' he said, especially where human intervention is needed to restore habitat or combat an invasive exotic species.
